00:31:33,103 --> 00:31:35,272
Oh, OK. I'll wait.

356
00:31:38,317 --> 00:31:40,361
- Bye, Walter.
- See you.

357
00:31:40,402 --> 00:31:42,655
- Bye, Marilyn.
- Bye, Ed.

358
00:32:01,549 --> 00:32:03,634
Sit down, son.

