00:33:40,189 --> 00:33:45,110
So don't try this strong-armed cowboy
crap on me, cos it won't do squat!

381
00:33:45,194 --> 00:33:47,238
Nooo!

382
00:33:56,622 --> 00:33:59,416
So, anyway, after med school,

383
00:33:59,500 --> 00:34:03,420
